Fukurama-Class

use this class as parent to force, control and simplify...
 - method- and function-signatures at compiletme
 - the usage of the strict and warnings pragmas
 
 and to make it possible...
  - to use strict datatypes at runtime

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install


SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the perldoc command.

    perldoc Fukurama::Class

You can also look for information at:

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/Fukurama-Class

    CPAN Request Tracker:
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=Fukurama-Class

    AnnoCPAN, annotated CPAN documentation:
        http://annocpan.org/dist/Fukurama-Class

    CPAN Ratings:
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/Fukurama-Class

